,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"什麼東西？　我現在在做準備……\n……只能一下下喔","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-027-002","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"透子","body":"是人家之前用手機拍的東西……\n你看，這個這個！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-027-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"……呃？　這是透子你嗎？\n為什麼打扮成這樣啊……呵呵","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-027-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"透子","body":"啊哈哈，蘭學姊笑出來了－！\n人家贏了～！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-027-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"透子","body":"是不是超適合人家的！\n這是人家生日那天大家送的禮物！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-027-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"透子","body":"哎呀－這個真的，不論看幾次都超爆笑的說～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-027-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"……話說，你為什麼要打扮成那樣？\n是玩遊戲輸了要受處罰嗎？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-027-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"透子","body":"才不是！\n真的是禮物啦～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-027-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"透子","body":"那天真心超爆笑，\n人家笑到肚子好痛～！\n真的超開心的說－","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-027-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"是嗎，這樣啊……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"smile03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-027-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"（原來很開心嗎，這個……\n我恐怕不太能理解……）","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-027-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"透子","body":"嗯－，像這樣開心大笑度過特別的一天，\n感覺真的超讚的","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-027-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"……這樣啊。\n也是，那這樣也很好吧？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-027-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"雖然我的感覺和透子的不太一樣，\n不過對透子來說，那就是你所謂的「讚」對吧","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-027-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"透子","body":"那還用說－！\n因為真心超讚到不行，人家重看了這些照片好幾次！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-027-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"透子","body":"啊！！\n對了對了蘭學姊，你不覺得待會LIVE，\n如果打扮成這樣上台氣氛會超嗨嗎！？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-027-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"透子","body":"這樣超引人注目一